headline: Design Software Stocks Q4 Results: Benchmarking Procore (NYSE:PCOR)
summary: The end of an earnings season can be a great time to discover new stocks and assess how companies are handling the current business environment. Let’s take a look at how Procore (NYSE:PCOR) and the rest of the design software stocks fared in Q4.
